643
00:33:47,450 --> 00:33:49,420
Sometimes I wonder,

644
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:52,080
in the past,

645
00:33:52,080 --> 00:33:53,860
how rich and prosperous our life was.

646
00:33:54,610 --> 00:33:56,820
Even if we've spent all our family fortune now,

647
00:33:57,130 --> 00:33:59,100
we still have money to buy such a good house

648
00:33:59,560 --> 00:34:00,790
