679
00:36:26,330 --> 00:36:27,990
Cui Jiu,

680
00:36:28,770 --> 00:36:29,890
I often see you

681
00:36:29,890 --> 00:36:31,290
playing Go

682
00:36:31,290 --> 00:36:32,870
with Lord Huaiyang.

683
00:36:33,890 --> 00:36:35,100
I thought you

684
00:36:35,330 --> 00:36:37,180
received this appreciation

