699
00:37:08,850 --> 00:37:09,690
Take it.

700
00:37:10,890 --> 00:37:11,730
Thank you.

701
00:37:12,600 --> 00:37:14,070
- Thank you.
- Take it.

702
00:37:23,260 --> 00:37:24,890
