710
00:37:52,040 --> 00:37:54,070
Just keep the money.

711
00:37:54,850 --> 00:37:56,180
- Thank you, My Lord.
- Well done.

712
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:57,880
Thank you, My Lord.

713
00:38:00,730 --> 00:38:02,040
Please keep

714
00:38:02,040 --> 00:38:03,950
