719
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:18,820
(Cui Mansion)

720
00:38:27,890 --> 00:38:28,730
Master.

721
00:38:32,290 --> 00:38:33,130
Master.

722
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:35,780
What if Ms. Liu is serious

723
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:37,660
and scolds you?

724
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:41,870
