725
00:38:43,520 --> 00:38:44,830
It doesn't matter if she scolds me.

726
00:38:45,810 --> 00:38:47,350
She won't turn down the money anyway.

727
00:38:49,450 --> 00:38:50,290
Yes.

728
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,040
What's going on?

729
00:39:01,250 --> 00:39:02,160
Nanny Li,

730
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:03,000
Moru,

731
00:39:03,450 --> 00:39:04,350
you both leave first.

732
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:06,120
Unless I say so,

733
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:06,960
stay out.

734
00:39:20,560 --> 00:39:21,620
What's the matter, Miantang?

735
00:39:24,200 --> 00:39:25,040
Jiu,

736
00:39:25,520 --> 00:39:26,950
is there something you want to tell me?

737
00:39:27,810 --> 00:39:29,510
Who upset you, Miantang?

738
00:39:30,770 --> 00:39:32,300
How long do you plan to hide it from me?

739
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:34,220
What did I hide?

740
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,700
I watched a Go match today

741
00:39:37,810 --> 00:39:39,180
at a restaurant in the west of the town.

742
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:46,260
So... you know that?

743
00:39:46,930 --> 00:39:47,770
Yes.

744
00:39:48,450 --> 00:39:50,580
I know you have been lying to me.

745
00:39:51,250 --> 00:39:53,080
I know the money you bring home every day

746
00:39:53,080 --> 00:39:54,660
is not from winning the Go.

747
00:39:55,370 --> 00:39:56,260
I also know

748
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:57,830
that you consort the influential officials,

749
00:40:00,330 --> 00:40:01,700
indulge in their idle pleasures,

750
00:40:03,250 --> 00:40:04,580
and flatter them all the time!

751
00:40:06,080 --> 00:40:07,220
What's wrong with that?

752
00:40:07,850 --> 00:40:09,390
I do it to earn money for our family.

753
00:40:09,680 --> 00:40:11,430
When did I ever need you to earn money?

754
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:14,740
I take care of this family

755
00:40:15,160 --> 00:40:16,770
so you can do

756
00:40:16,770 --> 00:40:18,300
what you love.

757
00:40:18,930 --> 00:40:19,770
However,

758
00:40:20,890 --> 00:40:22,770
to gain some benefits,

759
00:40:22,770 --> 00:40:23,990
you sullied the Go

760
00:40:24,730 --> 00:40:26,580
by deliberately losing to that dandy.

761
00:40:28,330 --> 00:40:29,170
Cui Jiu.

762
00:40:30,120 --> 00:40:31,910
Where is your dignity as a Go player?

763
00:40:32,200 --> 00:40:33,910
W-What dignity?

764
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:35,360
I was taking what...

765
00:40:39,640 --> 00:40:40,550
Mi-Miantang.

766
00:40:42,810 --> 00:40:43,950
From now on, I will…

767
00:40:45,930 --> 00:40:46,930
You still don't know

768
00:40:46,930 --> 00:40:48,350
