769
00:40:49,330 --> 00:40:50,580
I want to join the trade guild,

770
00:40:51,250 --> 00:40:52,640
but you strongly oppose

771
00:40:52,640 --> 00:40:54,430
and say it's a disgrace.

772
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:58,430
Yet, you are willing to give up your dignity
just to earn a living.

773
00:40:58,930 --> 00:40:59,930
As a couple,

774
00:40:59,930 --> 00:41:01,430
we're supposed to weather the storm together.

775
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:04,250
But it feels like I'm the only one

776
00:41:04,250 --> 00:41:05,580
living under your protection.

777
00:41:07,370 --> 00:41:08,290
You have never

778
00:41:08,290 --> 00:41:11,300
shared your concerns and grievances with me,

779
00:41:12,560 --> 00:41:13,680
and I have never

780
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:14,950
received your trust.

781
00:41:17,680 --> 00:41:19,430
Wasn't that what you said before?

782
00:41:20,120 --> 00:41:22,040
That there is only gratitude between us

783
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:23,450
and no need to weather the storm?

784
00:41:23,450 --> 00:41:24,660
But I want to.

785
00:41:27,330 --> 00:41:28,170
In the past,

786
00:41:29,410 --> 00:41:30,580
I misunderstood you.

787
00:41:32,520 --> 00:41:34,470
I didn't know that you'd rather suffer yourself

788
00:41:35,330 --> 00:41:37,550
