the members of the trade guild.

789
00:41:39,370 --> 00:41:41,510
I thought you were only focused on playing Go,

790
00:41:41,970 --> 00:41:43,430
not on handling household chores,

791
00:41:44,200 --> 00:41:45,780
and criticizing me.

792
00:41:46,600 --> 00:41:47,440
I...

793
00:41:48,680 --> 00:41:50,550
I relied on my memory loss

794
00:41:51,410 --> 00:41:53,410
to ignore all the good you did for me

795
00:41:53,410 --> 00:41:54,830
in the past.

796
00:41:56,250 --> 00:41:57,990
I only cared about my own feelings,

797
00:41:58,850 --> 00:41:59,930
but I never thought about

798
00:41:59,930 --> 00:42:01,390
how you felt,

799
00:42:03,120 --> 00:42:05,100
and said such harsh words to you.

800
00:42:08,330 --> 00:42:09,170
That is

801
00:42:10,560 --> 00:42:12,220
not the case.

802
00:42:14,770 --> 00:42:16,660
I didn't mean to blame you.

803
00:42:20,330 --> 00:42:21,170
Jiu.

804
00:42:24,720 --> 00:42:25,870
Let's forget

805
00:42:27,640 --> 00:42:28,770
all the misunderstandings

806
00:42:28,770 --> 00:42:29,910
and deceptions

807
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:32,550
from the past.

808
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,350
- Is it okay?
