809
00:42:38,290 --> 00:42:39,130
I...

810
00:42:40,330 --> 00:42:41,990
I want to get to know you again.

811
00:42:43,330 --> 00:42:44,260
I also want

812
00:42:45,200 --> 00:42:47,470
to be Cui Jiu's true wife.

813
00:42:48,290 --> 00:42:49,130
Is it okay?

814
00:42:52,970 --> 00:42:53,810
Okay.

815
00:42:55,450 --> 00:42:56,290
Miantang.

816
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:58,780
From now on,

817
00:42:59,450 --> 00:43:01,470
I will never consort with
the rich and powerful.

